snippet.title: The Disney Afternoon Collection - DuckTales Retrospective
snippet.description:
Let's jump back in time and take a closer look at one of the most beloved characters of all time: Scrooge McDuck from DuckTales!

DuckTales and DuckTales 2 are just two of the six games featured in The Disney Afternoon Collection, available now for PC, Xbox One and PlayStation 4. http://bit.ly/2oJIDpk

Subscribe to the Official Capcom Unity Channel: 
http://bit.ly/Qjb2MV
